overview.zh: Skeyer Chain是一个基于区块链技术的分布式内容集成服务平台。它通过区块链技术解决了当前内容产业的痛点。为内容产业参与者提供安全、稳定、可靠的内容发布和获取环境。
overview.en: Skeyer Chain is a decentralized content integration service platform based on blockchain technology. It solves the current content industry pain points through blockchain technology.  To provide participants in the content industry with a safe, stable and reliable content publishing and acquisition environmentand.
